## Brief description of the set cover problem.

Consider we have a collection of points, and a collection of sets, where each set contains a subset of the collection of points. 
Important is that a point can be in multiple of the sets.
To illustrate, consider the figure below.

[Figure of set cover problem](images/set cover problem.png)
